"""
Broward permit scraper/importer for leadflow.

Purpose:
- Scrape Broward municipal Accela permit portals, starting with Weston.
- Save raw permit payloads into raw_permits.
- Normalize usable permit records into normalized_permits.
- Save debug page sources/inventories so selector/search issues can be diagnosed.

Primary stable source right now:
- weston_accela

Known reality:
- Broward is not one clean countywide permit feed.
- Each city may need its own Accela/source config.
- This script is designed to support source-by-source expansion.

Run examples:
    python -m app.workers.scrape_broward_permits --source weston_accela --days-back 7 --visible --debug-pages
    python -m app.workers.scrape_broward_permits --source weston_accela --start 2026-04-24 --end 2026-04-24 --limit 0 --pages 25 --visible --debug-pages
    python -m app.workers.scrape_broward_permits --all-broward --days-back 30 --limit 0 --pages 25 --debug-pages
"""

